01  WS-AREA. 
05  WS-CODE PIC 9(5) VALUE 0. 
05  WS-DATA PIC X(100). 

PROCEDURE DIVISION. 
    PERFORM 100-INITIALIZE. 
    PERFORM 200-PROCESS-DATA. 
    PERFORM 300-TERMINATE. 
    STOP RUN. 

100-INITIALIZE SECTION. 
    MOVE ZERO TO WS-CODE. 
    MOVE SPACES TO WS-DATA. 

200-PROCESS-DATA SECTION. 
    DISPLAY "Enter data: " WITH NO ADVANCING. 
    ACCEPT WS-DATA. 
    IF WS-DATA = SPACES THEN 
        DISPLAY "No data entered" 
        GO TO 300-TERMINATE 
    END-IF. 
    COMPUTE WS-CODE = FUNCTION LENGTH(WS-DATA). 

300-TERMINATE SECTION. 
    DISPLAY "The length of data is: " WS-CODE. 
    GO TO 300-TERMINATE.